raw_data.name: The Salty Donut
raw_data.subtypes: Donut shop, Bakery, Cafe, Coffee shop

reviews_data.review_text: So excited that The Salty Donut has opened in Plaza Midwood! I’ve loved the South End location, and this one absolutely lives up to it. The space is super clean, the staff is incredibly friendly, and there are tons of donut options to choose from—all fresh and delicious. They also have sandwiches and a great coffee menu, making it an easy stop for breakfast or a casual bite. Plenty of indoor seating too, which makes it a great spot to hang out and enjoy your treat. Such a great addition to the neighborhood! 🍩✨
